                     tābot of <t:persName type="tabot" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9162TaklaHa">Takla Haymanot</t:persName> in the lower church for the local people.</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="description">219 Mss. photographed in 2006 (for the <t:placeName type="library" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0004HMML">Hill Museum and Microfilm Library</t:placeName>; s. also <t:ref target="http://ethiopia.deeds.utoronto.ca/about.html"/>).</t:ab>
        
